title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Burns/Leber/Birk
description: -- Nordo fills in for PA for the next couple days, Ryan Burns talks Gophers and National Signing Day, Ben Leber talks Vikings and Bears, Producer Brett brings the news, and Matt Birk talks the madness on Monday night with the Ravens, and looking ahead for the Vikings.
